      "pos": [
        7512,
        7695
      ],
      "content": "For more information about Azure AD Join please see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Extending cloud capabilities to Windows 10 devices through Azure Active Directory Join<ept id=\"p1\">](active-directory-azureadjoin-overview.md)</ept>."
    },
    {
      "content": "Enabling personally-owned devices for work with work accounts",
      "pos": [
        7699,
        7760
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "To support BYOD in the enterprise, Windows 10 gives the user the ability to “add a work or school account” to their PC, tablet or phone.",
      "pos": [
        7762,
        7898
      ]
