      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For organizations that don’t integrate their MDM with Azure AD, users can enroll the device into management manually via <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Settings<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> &gt; <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Accounts<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> &gt; <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Work access<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept>.",
      "pos": [
